and bullion dealers to begin doing business on the internet they set up a website to auction jewelry from their stores in  and later launched two further websites for auctioning watches and to allow jewelry manufactures and vendors to sell to each other and directly to the public they also set up a website to provide realtime price quotes for precious metals their revenues from their internet business began to show dramatic growth in  revenue to march  of that year was five times the revenue for their  fiscal year their acquisition of superior galleries and the success of superiors first auction under dgse ownership drove their share price up  to  in august  dgse operates thirty five retail locations eight dallas gold and silver exchange stores throughout the dallasfort worth metroplex bullion express in highland park chicago il charleston gold  diamond exchange in charleston sc and  stores branded as southern bullion coin  jewelry throughout the southeast us including alabama tennessee north carolina south carolina florida and georgia in april  dgse announces halt in trading of its public stock on amex  in june  dgse closes its superior gold and silver exchange store in woodland hills in july  dgse opens two new stores in dallasfort worth metroplex southlake tx and allen tx in november  dgse opened a new store in fort worth tx  in november  dgse companies announces the resumption of trading of its public stock on nyse mkt timelineedit this article needs additional citations for verification please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources unsourced material may be challenged and removed june  learn how and when to remove this template message   incorporation of american pacific mint  – rainbow rare coins founded  – rainbow rare coins changes name to dallas gold  silver exchange  – publicly traded american pacific mint acquires the assets of dallas gold  silver exchange  – dallas gold  silver exchange acquires its first texas pawn license to provide jewelry loans to its customers – dallas gold  silver exchange launches online auction platform  – dallas gold  silver exchange acquires national jewelry exchange a small pawnshop in carrolton texas  – dallas gold  silver exchange opens charleston south carolina location under the name charleston gold  diamond exchange  – dallas gold  silver exchange acquires fairchild international one of the largest wholesale fine watch companies in the united states  – us bullion exchange is launched to handle trading and execution of all precious metals transactions system wide for all dgse companies usbe provides an internetbased trading platform for all dgse customers   parent company’s name changed to dgse companies inc  – dallas gold  silver exchange acquires the assets of euless gold  silver and opens dallas gold  silver exchange fort wortheuless location   dgse companies inc lists on the american stock exchange  – the second dallas area national pawn store is opened  – american gold  silver exchange is launched with national advertising rollout allowing individuals from anywhere to send jewelry and precious metals to dgse for purchase  – superior estate buyers is launched and conducts its first remote buying events  – dgse companies inc acquire superior galleries one of the united states oldest and largest numismatic auction houses   superior galleries conducts its first jewelry and fine time piece auction in beverly hills california  – superior precious metals is launched to service precious metals and rare coin retail customers   superior gold  diamond exchange is opened in woodland hills california   dgse companies inc launches a charitable fundraising company under the name a chance to give   dgse bullion express concept is introduced new store opened in preston center in dallas texas   second dgse bullion express is opened in north dallas   dgse companies inc opens fifth dallasarea location in arlington   dgse companies inc opens a bullion express store in highland park chicago illinois   dgse companies inc opens a bullion express store in atlanta georgias buckhead district   securities and exchange commission sec announces investigation into dgse accounting irregularities   dgse companies inc opens th dfw area location in southlake texas   dgse companies inc opens th dfw area location in allen texas   dgse companies inc opens th dfw area location in fort worth texas using some artwork and jewelry cases from the now defunct superior galleries   dgse companies inc opens nd atlanta area location in cumming georgia branded as southern bullion coin  jewelry referencesedit  a b schmidt rob  the ecommerce ticket for coin and bullion investors these shares turn collectibles into investibles coin connoisseur magazine archived from the original on  retrieved    dallas gold  silver exchange inc dallas business journal  retrieved  dead link  la briefly daily news of los angeles  retrieved    form ksb sec filing dgse companies inc  archived from the original on  retrieved    american pacific mint plans move to dallas los angeles times  retrieved    name change okd american metal market  retrieved  dead link  dallas gold  silver exchange changes name to dgse dallas business journal  retrieved    dallas gold and silver exchange reports internet growth dallas business journal  retrieved    dgse up  percent speeple news  retrieved    dgse halts trading yahoofinance   check date values in date help  wwwdgsecom  archived from the original on    dgse companies inc  dallas gold  silver exchange opens fort worth location  traders  dgse companies inc  dgse announces resumption of trading on nyse mkt  traders  chicagoland’s first gold investment boutique “bullion express” opens in highland parkpermanent dead link  dgse companies inc opens “bullion express” retail boutique in atlanta’s buckhead district  yahoo finance  dallas gold  silver exchange opens location in southlake tx  dallas gold  silver exchange opens seventh dfw location in allen te