ld be expected to close in the  rd quarter of  dgse expects the acquisition to bring promising revenue and earnings accretion to shareholders going forward national and its affiliates have a store footprint including stores in arizona north carolina oklahoma and texas national is based in austin texas it was founded in  by its current ceo courtland corky l logue jr logue logue has a long history in founding and operating pawnshops including ezpawn and ezcorp nasdaq ezpw we continue to explore new opportunities and agreements with potential partners who are excited about being a part of dgses future we believe this positions dgse to generate an attractive total shareholder return over the long term stated john loftus dgses president chairman and chief executive officer elemetal recycling update as announced on april   dgse has also entered into a nonbinding letter of intent to acquire certain tangible personalproperty assets of elemetal recycling llc from elemetal llc this transaction is progressing well with dgse working to complete requisite due diligence financing and a definitive agreement profits and retailoperations update dgse expects to post a profit in the second quarter of  and show continued operational improvement though there is still much to be done to build the business to its full potential and maximize shareholder value dgse anticipates getting smarter with each customer interaction educating its sales staff on customers preferred products if you liked this article you might like dgse companies inc stock downgraded dgse dgse companies amexdgse has been downgraded by thestreet ratings from from a buy to hold thestreet wire sep    am edt  stocks setting up to break out these stocks look poised to break out and trade higher from current prices roberto pedone jun    pm edt dgse companies inc stock upgraded dgse dgse companies amexdgse has been upgraded by thestreet ratings from a hold to buy thestreet wire jun    am edt dgse on the block it hires southwe